						<div class="postbody">Perhaps it could be predicted in advance if some sort of queuing/timestamp system were used. However, I'm going for a relatively simple model, where one opcode is executed at a time and the PPU/APU/MMC states are updated on each clock cycle. Thus, the MMC routine would be called every single cycle to decrement (or increment) the clock cycle counter.</div>

